description: Integral shoot of Zack Lemec's classic scene 'Zack Fucks'. Producer & Owner of Maskurbate, Pascal, put together all the footage shot that day so Zack's fan can see everything that happened. From the behind-the-scene to some cool unseen point of views, it's a must see for the fans of Maskurbate's most popular model, Zack Lemec.
title: Zack Fucks - Integral Shoot
